PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the ENGLISH RIVER BAND, of a total of 3,974.86 hectares of land in Saskatchewan, including mines and minerals, as additions to Elak Dase Indian Reserve No. 192A, Knee Lake Indian Reserve No. 192B, Dipper Rapids Indian Reserve No. 192C and Wapachewunak Lake Indian Reserve No. 192D.
